---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Section 21 Approval | Mount Kush Cannabis Lifestyle Store"
  description="Mount Kush is a Section 21 approved collection point. View our approval documentation and compliance information."
  ogImage="/images/Section 21.jpg"
>

  <!-- ══ PAGE HERO ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Compliance & Approval</div>
      <h1 class="display-md">Section 21 Approval</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:1rem;">
        Mount Kush is a Section 21 approved collection point, operating in compliance
        with South African regulatory requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ CONTENT ════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--purple-deep);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:var(--gold-bright);">Approved Collection Point</strong><br/><br/>
          Mount Kush holds Section 21 approval under the Medicines and Related Substances Act, 101 of 1965, as administered by the South African Health Products Regulatory Authority (SAHPRA). This approval designates Mount Kush as an authorised collection point operating within the applicable regulatory framework.
        </div>

        <h2>Our Approval</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush is committed to operating transparently and in full compliance with South African law. Our Section 21 approval reflects this commitment and provides our customers with confidence that they are engaging with a regulated, accountable business.</p>

        <img
          src="/images/Section 21.jpg"
          alt="Mount Kush Section 21 Approval Certificate"
          style="width:100%; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); margin:2rem 0; display:block;"
          loading="lazy"
        />

        <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
        <p>As a customer, our Section 21 approved status means:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You are transacting with an operator that has been reviewed and approved by the relevant regulatory authority.</li>
          <li>Mount Kush operates within a defined compliance framework, not outside it.</li>
          <li>Our collection point designation is formal, documented, and maintained in accordance with regulatory requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Adult Customers Only</h2>
        <p>All products and services offered by Mount Kush — including those available at our Section 21 approved collection point — are sold exclusively to adults 18 years of age and older. Age verification may be required at the point of collection.</p>
        <p>Mount Kush does not sell to minors under any circumstances.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:white;">Questions about our approval?</strong><br/>
          Contact us on WhatsApp at <a href="https://wa.me/27639260217" style="color:var(--gold-bright);">063 926 0217</a>.
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top:3rem; display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="/stores" class="btn btn-outline-gold">Find Our Stores →</a>
          <a href="/responsible-use" class="btn btn-outline-white">Responsible Use</a>
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top:2rem; font-size:0.82rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
          Mount Kush operates in compliance with the Medicines and Related Substances Act, 101 of 1965, the Cannabis for Private Purposes Act, 2024, and all applicable South African law. Adults only. 18+.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
